g.title: level_map
g.text: Item and room map for the Terminus game.
Labeled arrows represent tasks that need to be completed before advancing to the next room.
Dotted arrows are rooms that are connected but that you cannot move into.
Dashed lines mean originally hidden until a task is completed.
